Distribution and Phenology (
Fig. 61
). This species is restricted to the Paraná and Uruguay river basins from Brazil (Minas Gerais to Rio Grande do Sul), Paraguay (Alto Paraná), Argentina (Misiones) and Uruguay (Montevideo) (
Fig. 61
), in deciduous forest reaching 1000m . Based on collection data, this species has been registered during all months, suggesting several continuous generations throughout the year.
